#X text -57 -81 Then either click [output 0] to set the pin to input
mode and bang the [gpio] to make it read the pin and emit the current
value \,;
#X text -58 -31 or click [output 1] to set the pin to output mode and
send 0 or 1 to the [gpio] to set the pin to that output level.;
